These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: soy-milk, almond-milk
Cigar: bongani, blend
1. Cigar:bongani is in an even position##4
2. Cigar:blend == Beverage:almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | soy-milk |
| Cigar     | blend    | bongani   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
City: rome, san-francisco
Pet: hamster, hedgehog
1. Pet:hamster is in an odd position##4
2. City:san-francisco is on the left of City:rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| City   | san-francisco | rome        |
| Pet      | hamster  | hedgehog |

 #################################
 
