.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-10::.
Cigar: bolivar, havana
City: miami, venice
1. City:venice == Cigar:havana##1
2. City:miami is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |     2     |
| Cigar          | havana | bolivar |
| City   | venice | miami   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-11::.
